name: R5-ImagingStudy-R4-ImagingStudy
title: Concept map to convert a FHIR R5 ImagingStudy into FHIR R4

element.display: A set of images produced in single study (one or more series of references images)

target.display: A set of images produced in single study (one or more series of references images)
target.comment: R5 `ImagingStudy` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ImagingStudy`
R5 `ImagingStudy.basedOn` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ImagingStudy.basedOn`
R5 `ImagingStudy.contained` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ImagingStudy.contained`
R5 `ImagingStudy.description` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ImagingStudy.description`

element.display: Encounter with which this imaging study is associated

target.display: Encounter with which this imaging study is associated
target.comment: R5 `ImagingStudy.encounter` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ImagingStudy.encounter`
R5 `ImagingStudy.endpoint` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ImagingStudy.endpoint`

R5 `ImagingStudy.extension` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget to R4 `ImagingStudy.extension` - extension has change due to type change: R5 `extension` `Extension` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget for R4 `extension`
R5 `ImagingStudy.id` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ImagingStudy.id`
R5 `ImagingStudy.identifier` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ImagingStudy.identifier`

element.display: A set of rules under which this content was created

target.display: A set of rules under which this content was created
target.comment: R5 `ImagingStudy.implicitRules` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ImagingStudy.implicitRules`

R5 `ImagingStudy.language` maps as SourceIsNarrowerThanTarget to R4 `ImagingStudy.language` - language changed the binding strength from Required to Preferred; language has change due to type change: R5 `language` `code` maps as SourceIsNarrowerThanTarget for R4 `language`
R5 `ImagingStudy.location` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ImagingStudy.location`
R5 `ImagingStudy.meta` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ImagingStudy.meta`

element.display: All of the distinct values for series' modalities

target.display: All series modality if actual acquisition modalities
target.comment: R5 `ImagingStudy.modality` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget to R4 `ImagingStudy.modality` - modality has change due to type change: R5 modality CodeableConcept has no equivalent or mapped type in R4 modality

R5 `ImagingStudy.modifierExtension` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget to R4 `ImagingStudy.modifierExtension` - modifierExtension has change due to type change: R5 `modifierExtension` `Extension` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget for R4 `modifierExtension`
R5 `ImagingStudy.note` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget to R4 `ImagingStudy.note` - note has change due to type change: R5 `note` `Annotation` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget for R4 `note`
R5 `ImagingStudy.numberOfInstances` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ImagingStudy.numberOfInstances`
R5 `ImagingStudy.numberOfSeries` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ImagingStudy.numberOfSeries`

R5 `ImagingStudy.procedure` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget to R4 `ImagingStudy.procedureCode` - procedureCode changed the binding strength from Preferred to Extensible; procedureCode has change due to type change: R5 procedure CodeableReference has no equivalent or mapped type in R4 procedureCode

R5 `ImagingStudy.procedure` maps as RelatedTo to R4 `ImagingStudy.procedureReference` - procedureReference changed from array to scalar (max cardinality from * to 1); procedureReference removed a binding requirement - Preferred http://loinc.org/vs/loinc-rsna-radiology-playbook; procedureReference has change due to type change: R5 procedure CodeableReference has no equivalent or mapped type in R4 procedureReference

R5 `ImagingStudy.reason` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget to R4 `ImagingStudy.reasonCode` - reasonCode has change due to type change: R5 reason CodeableReference has no equivalent or mapped type in R4 reasonCode

R5 `ImagingStudy.reason` maps as RelatedTo to R4 `ImagingStudy.reasonReference` - reasonReference removed a binding requirement - Example http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/procedure-reason; reasonReference has change due to type change: R5 reason CodeableReference has no equivalent or mapped type in R4 reasonReference
R5 `ImagingStudy.referrer` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ImagingStudy.referrer`
